{"branchingScenario":{"content":[{"type":{"library":"H5P.AdvancedText 1.1","params":{"text":"<p>Find a news story of an incident of police-perpetrated violence that occurred in your community - use search terms such as place name, the name of your local policing bodies, \u2018inquiry\u2019, and \u2018investigation\u2019 as a good place to start.<\/p>\n"},"subContentId":"0b23e96f-dbed-4d1b-a437-ba78fff76ead","metadata":{"contentType":"Text","license":"U","title":"Finding materials"}},"showContentTitle":false,"forceContentFinished":"useBehavioural","feedback":{"subtitle":""},"contentBehaviour":"useBehavioural","nextContentId":1},{"type":{"library":"H5P.AdvancedText 1.1","params":{"text":"<p>Take some time to look at how the media describes the incident, and take note of the following:<\/p>\n"},"subContentId":"31a6a3bb-8395-40ea-8ec9-375dc0ec15bd","metadata":{"contentType":"Text","license":"U","title":"Taking notes"}},"showContentTitle":false,"forceContentFinished":"useBehavioural","feedback":{"subtitle":""},"contentBehaviour":"useBehavioural","nextContentId":2},{"type":{"library":"H5P.AdvancedText 1.1","params":{"text":"<p>Whose perspective is foregrounded in the aritcle(s)?&nbsp;<\/p>\n"},"subContentId":"a7855369-6c45-45e2-b07b-2d3ec28878dd","metadata":{"contentType":"Text","license":"U","title":"Perspective"}},"showContentTitle":false,"forceContentFinished":"useBehavioural","feedback":{"subtitle":""},"contentBehaviour":"useBehavioural","nextContentId":3},{"type":{"library":"H5P.AdvancedText 1.1","params":{"text":"<p>Where does the information about what happened come from - police, victims, witnesses, investigative bodies?<\/p>\n"},"subContentId":"4ef644a6-9117-4629-9e26-ded199b35519","metadata":{"contentType":"Text","license":"U","title":"Sources"}},"showContentTitle":false,"forceContentFinished":"useBehavioural","feedback":{"subtitle":""},"contentBehaviour":"useBehavioural","nextContentId":4},{"type":{"library":"H5P.AdvancedText 1.1","params":{"text":"<p>Can you take all the information at face value or is there extraneous contextual information provided about the people involved - for example, is the arrest history of the victim-survivor on unrelated incidents included?<\/p>\n"},"subContentId":"98eaaec0-d54a-4956-88fc-fa835993bfa4","metadata":{"contentType":"Text","license":"U","title":"Evaluation"}},"showContentTitle":false,"forceContentFinished":"useBehavioural","feedback":{"subtitle":""},"contentBehaviour":"useBehavioural","nextContentId":5},{"type":{"library":"H5P.AdvancedText 1.1","params":{"text":"<p>Does the article conform to any of the 7 editorial principles of YEGPVA records mentioned above?<\/p>\n"},"subContentId":"9762c952-5fba-4ded-a1cd-3c37d650457a","metadata":{"contentType":"Text","license":"U","title":"Principles"}},"showContentTitle":false,"forceContentFinished":"useBehavioural","feedback":{"subtitle":""},"contentBehaviour":"useBehavioural","nextContentId":6},{"type":{"library":"H5P.AdvancedText 1.1","params":{"text":"<p>If you feel that the article does not conform to the principles, write an alternative version of this event. What additional information is missing to get the complete picture? And hypothetically, how could it be obtained?<\/p>\n"},"subContentId":"b0e701a9-cb21-4ea0-b239-b678492f1304","metadata":{"contentType":"Text","license":"U","title":"Revision"}},"showContentTitle":false,"forceContentFinished":"useBehavioural","feedback":{"subtitle":""},"contentBehaviour":"useBehavioural","nextContentId":-1}],"endScreens":[{"endScreenTitle":"","endScreenSubtitle":"","contentId":-1,"endScreenScore":0}],"scoringOptionGroup":{"scoringOption":"no-score","includeInteractionsScores":true},"startScreen":{"startScreenTitle":"<p>Exercise: Reconstructing mainstream narratives<\/p>\n","startScreenSubtitle":""},"behaviour":{"enableBackwardsNavigation":true,"forceContentFinished":false},"l10n":{"startScreenButtonText":"Start the course","endScreenButtonText":"Restart the course","backButtonText":"Back","proceedButtonText":"Proceed","disableProceedButtonText":"Require to complete the current module","replayButtonText":"Replay the video","scoreText":"Your score:","fullscreenAria":"Fullscreen"}}}